➜公益永不止步！“美丽东南 书绘未来”持续助力寿宁教育扶贫
http://www.sohu.com/a/429013760_99994080	45808
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201102/a77ef0ee561041f88e75f8aa4754c1bf.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201102/9320793181f94d9cb7599605e5cf5929.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>本文编辑：</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201102/53f2b3d36faa43c19566f915aa6cb08b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>写在前面：</strong></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
